#. ちょっと待って。
#. 茶柱さんはカゴの中で座っていたんじゃないんだ。
msgctxt "0000 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"Wait just a minute, Tenko wasn't sitting\n"
"down inside the cage."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltSTRONG>亀のような体勢<CLT=cltNORMAL>になっていたんだよ。
#. 地面に置いた<CLT=cltSTRONG>目印の石<CLT=cltNORMAL>を額に付ける恰好でね。
msgctxt "0001 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"She was <CLT=cltSTRONG>bent over<CLT=cltNORMAL> with her\n"
"forehead against the <CLT=cltSTRONG>marker stone<CLT=cltNORMAL>."
msgstr ""

#. しかも、あのカゴは高さが１メートルくらいあった。
msgctxt "0002 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "And the cage itself was about three feet tall."
msgstr ""

#. 中で亀の体勢になっている茶柱さんを刺すには、
#. 刃渡り１５センチのカマじゃ届かないよ。
msgctxt "0003 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"The sickle's blade was too short to reach\n"
"Tenko while she was in that position."
msgstr ""

#. じゃあ…また間違ったの？
#. も、もう…恥ずかしくて生きていけないよぉ…
msgctxt "0004 | c03_217_000 | C014_Iruma"
msgid ""
"Then...I messed up again? How could\n"
"this happen? I'm so embarrassed..."
msgstr ""

#. 大丈夫だよ！　入間ちゃんが恥ずかしい人間なのは、
#. みんなとっくに知ってるし！
msgctxt "0005 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"No worries, Miu! Everyone already knows\n"
"you're an embarrassment to the human race!"
msgstr ""

#. うんっ、安心していいよっ！
msgctxt "0006 | c03_217_000 | C004_Gokuh"
msgid "Yeah! No worries!"
msgstr ""

#. ひいいっ！　は、恥ずかしいっ！
msgctxt "0007 | c03_217_000 | C014_Iruma"
msgid "Heeeeeee! How...how embarrassing!"
msgstr ""

#. ただ、今の最原クンの話だと、
#. 茶柱さんをカゴ越しに刺すのは不可能という事ですよね。
msgctxt "0008 | c03_217_000 | C007_Ki-Bo"
msgid ""
"If Shuichi is right, then it's impossible for\n"
"Tenko to have been killed through the cage."
msgstr ""

#. だったら、降霊術の最中に殺せねーじゃねーか。
#. だって、あいつはずっとカゴの中にいたんだろ？
msgctxt "0009 | c03_217_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"She couldn't have been killed during the \n"
"seance since she was in the cage, right?"
msgstr ""

#. そもそも、降霊術中に彼女が刺し殺されたなら、
#. カゴを覆っていた白い布も貫通されているはずだよネ。
msgctxt "0010 | c03_217_000 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"If she was killed then, the cloth over \n"
"the cage would have been pierced."
msgstr ""

#. でも、床下から殺した可能性もないんでしょ？
#. そうすると、もう完全に不可能じゃない？
msgctxt "0011 | c03_217_000 | C012_Shiro"
msgid ""
"Not during the seance or from below\n"
"the floor... Then it's impossible, isn't it?"
msgstr ""

#. …生きている人間にはね。
msgctxt "0012 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid "...Yeah, for a living person."
msgstr ""

#. …あ？
msgctxt "0013 | c03_217_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid "Huh...?"
msgstr ""

#. にしし…茶柱ちゃんを殺したのは、
#. 死んだアンジーちゃんの霊だったりして…
msgctxt "0014 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"Nee-heehee... What if Angie's spirit\n"
"killed Tenko?"
msgstr ""

#. な、何言ってやがんだっ！
#. そそ、そんな訳ねーだろうがっ！
msgctxt "0015 | c03_217_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"Wh-What are you talking about!?\n"
"Th-Th-That's not possible!"
msgstr ""

#. いや、わからないよ？
#. 人間に不可能な事でも、<CLT=cltSTRONG>霊<CLT=cltNORMAL>なら可能だろうしね。
msgctxt "0016 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"We don't know that. Some things are\n"
"impossible for a human, but not for a spirit."
msgstr ""

#. バ、バカ言ってんじゃねー！
#. なな、何が霊だっ！
msgctxt "0017 | c03_217_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"D-Don't say stupid stuff like that!\n"
"S-S-Screw spirits!"
msgstr ""

#. …ねぇ、いい加減にしてよ。
msgctxt "0018 | c03_217_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid "...Stop that now."
msgstr ""

#. ………………
msgctxt "0019 | c03_217_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. アンジーの霊が…転子を殺したじゃと？
#. そ、それは…なぜじゃ？
msgctxt "0020 | c03_217_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "Angie's spirit...killed Tenko? Wh-Why...?"
msgstr ""

#. …夢野さん？
msgctxt "0021 | c03_217_000 | C004_Gokuh"
msgid "Himiko?"
msgstr ""

#. なぜ…アンジーの霊が転子を殺すんじゃ？
msgctxt "0022 | c03_217_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "Why would Angie's spirit kill Tenko?"
msgstr ""

#. たとえば、アンジーちゃんを殺したのが茶柱ちゃんで、
#. それを恨んだアンジーちゃんの霊がやり返して――
msgctxt "0023 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"What if Tenko killed Angie, and then \n"
"Angie's spirit came back for reven—"
msgstr ""

#. だから、ちげーって言ってんだろっ！
#. 犯人が幽霊なんて…そんな訳ねーだろ！！
msgctxt "0024 | c03_217_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"Like I said, that's impossible!\n"
"Spirits can't be culprits!"
msgstr ""

#. だったら、あの不可能な状況下で、
#. 犯人はどうやって茶柱ちゃんを殺したの？
msgctxt "0025 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"Then explain how the culprit killed Tenko\n"
"under these impossible circumstances."
msgstr ""

#. だ、だから…それはだな…
msgctxt "0026 | c03_217_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid "W-Well, uh..."
msgstr ""

#. ほーら、わからないでしょ？
#. やっぱり、あれは霊の仕業としか――
msgctxt "0027 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"See? You can't explain, can you?\n"
"Only a spirit could have done th—"
msgstr ""

#. ま、待て！　そうだ！
#. 犯人はカゴの中に隠れてたんじゃねーのか！？
msgctxt "0028 | c03_217_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"W-Wait, I know! What if the culprit \n"
"was hiding inside the cage!?"
msgstr ""

#. ほら、同じカゴの中にいたら、
#. 降霊術中に茶柱を刺し殺す事もできんだろ！
msgctxt "0029 | c03_217_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"If they were in there, they coulda\n"
"stabbed Tenko during the seance!"
msgstr ""

#. いや、カゴの中にもう１人いたら、
#. さすがに僕らも気付いて――
msgctxt "0030 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"No, if there was someone else\n"
"in the cage, we would've noticed—"
msgstr ""

#. 私も百田と同じ意見だよ。
#. 犯人はあのカゴの中にいたんだと思う。
msgctxt "0031 | c03_217_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"I agree with Kaito. The culprit could have\n"
"been inside the cage."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>…えっ？
msgctxt "0032 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "<CLT=cltMIND>...You do?"
msgstr ""

#. いやいや、それはあり得ないヨ。
#. カゴの中には犯人が隠れるスペースなんてないヨ。
msgctxt "0033 | c03_217_000 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"Nonsense. There was no space in\n"
"the cage for the culprit to hide."
msgstr ""

#. もし<CLT=cltSTRONG>“あいつ”<CLT=cltNORMAL>が犯人だとしたら、
#. そもそも隠れる必要すらないんだよ。
msgctxt "0034 | c03_217_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"Maybe the <CLT=cltSTRONG>culprit<CLT=cltNORMAL> wouldn't need\n"
"to hide in the first place."
msgstr ""

#. …え？
msgctxt "0035 | c03_217_000 | C006_Shing"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

#. それに“あいつ”なら
#. いつでもカゴの中で殺す事ができたはずだから…
msgctxt "0036 | c03_217_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"Also, the culprit could've killed her in the\n"
"cage at any time."
msgstr ""

#. 今の疑問は一気にクリアになると思うけど？
msgctxt "0037 | c03_217_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid "I think you know what I'm getting at, right?"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>もしかして、
#. 春川さんの言う“あいつ”って…
msgctxt "0038 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>The \"they\" she's\n"
"referring to..."
msgstr ""

#. まさか…夢野さんが…？
msgctxt "0039 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "Do you mean...Himiko?"
msgstr ""

#. なぜウチの事を疑うんじゃ…
msgctxt "0040 | c03_217_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "Why are you suspecting me?"
msgstr ""

#. ウチが転子を殺すわけないっ！
msgctxt "0041 | c03_217_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "I would never kill Tenko!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>みんなの冷ややかな視線…
#. 僕の印象が悪くなったみたいだ…
#. <CLT=cltNORMAL>
msgctxt "0042 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>Everyone's staring at me... \n"
"I screwed up, they think I'm a fraud... \n"
"<CLT=cltNORMAL>"
msgstr ""

#. やっぱり、アンジーさんの霊の仕業なのかな…
msgctxt "0043 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "Do you mean...Angie's ghost?"
msgstr ""

#. は？
#. あんたもそんなくだらない事考えてんの？
msgctxt "0044 | c03_217_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"Can you stop thinking about such stupid\n"
"things?"
msgstr ""

#. そ、そうだっ！
#. ゆ、幽霊が犯人なんて…あってたまるか！
msgctxt "0045 | c03_217_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"Th-That's right! S-Spirits can't be\n"
"culprits...that's not how it works!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>みんなの冷ややかな視線…
#. 僕の印象が悪くなったみたいだ…
#. <CLT=cltNORMAL>
msgctxt "0046 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>Everyone's staring at me... \n"
"I screwed up, they think I'm a fraud... \n"
"<CLT=cltNORMAL>"
msgstr ""

#. …最原もわからないの？
#. 探偵なんだから、これぐらい気付きなよ。
msgctxt "0047 | c03_217_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"You really don't know? I thought at least a\n"
"detective like you could figure it out."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>みんなの冷ややかな視線…
#. 僕の印象が悪くなったみたいだ…
#. <CLT=cltNORMAL>
msgctxt "0048 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>Everyone's staring at me... \n"
"I screwed up, they think I'm a fraud... \n"
"<CLT=cltNORMAL>"
msgstr ""

#. …違うよ。
#. カゴの中にいる茶柱をいつでも殺せたのは誰？
msgctxt "0049 | c03_217_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"...Wrong. Who could have killed Tenko\n"
"inside the cage at any time?"
msgstr ""

#. ちょっとした謎謎だよ。
#. あんたって頭固いんだね。探偵のくせに。
msgctxt "0050 | c03_217_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"I don't get you. \n"
"You're really narrow-minded for a detective."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>みんなの冷ややかな視線…
#. 僕の印象が悪くなったみたいだ…
#. <CLT=cltNORMAL>
msgctxt "0051 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>Everyone's staring at me... \n"
"I screwed up, they think I'm a fraud... \n"
"<CLT=cltNORMAL>"
msgstr ""

#. カゴの中の茶柱を
#. 殺す事ができたのは誰？
msgctxt "0052 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"Who could have killed Tenko\n"
"from inside the cage?"
msgstr ""

#. 春川さんが言う“あいつ”って、
#. もしかして、<CLT=cltSTRONG>茶柱さん<CLT=cltNORMAL>自身の事？
msgctxt "0053 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"I believe Maki is referring to\n"
"<CLT=cltSTRONG>Tenko<CLT=cltNORMAL> herself."
msgstr ""

#. んあっ？　なんじゃと！？
msgctxt "0054 | c03_217_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "Nyeh!? What did you say!?"
msgstr ""

#. 犯人が茶柱さん自身って…どういう事？
msgctxt "0055 | c03_217_000 | C012_Shiro"
msgid "Are you saying...Tenko is the culprit?"
msgstr ""

#. …<CLT=cltSTRONG>自殺<CLT=cltNORMAL>って事だよ。
msgctxt "0056 | c03_217_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid "...She committed <CLT=cltSTRONG>suicide<CLT=cltNORMAL>."
msgstr ""

#. じ、自殺っ！？
msgctxt "0057 | c03_217_000 | C004_Gokuh"
msgid "S-Suicide!?"
msgstr ""

#. あいつが自殺だとすると、
#. 色んな疑問点が一気に解消されるんだよ。
msgctxt "0058 | c03_217_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"If she committed suicide, it would explain\n"
"a lot of things we couldn't figure out."
msgstr ""

#. カゴの中にこっそりカマを持ち込んで、
#. 降霊術の最中に自分を刺せばいいだけだから…
msgctxt "0059 | c03_217_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"She volunteered to be in the cage, and then\n"
"stabbed herself during the seance."
msgstr ""

#. 暗闇だろうが、別に関係ない。
msgctxt "0060 | c03_217_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid "It wouldn't matter how dark the room was."
msgstr ""

#. でもよ、凶器のカマは床下に落ちてたんだろ？
msgctxt "0061 | c03_217_000 | C014_Iruma"
msgid ""
"But the sickle she was stabbed with\n"
"was under the floor, right?"
msgstr ""

#. 茶柱が自分で自分を刺したなら、
#. 凶器はカゴの中に落ちてるはずじゃねーか？
msgctxt "0062 | c03_217_000 | C014_Iruma"
msgid ""
"If Tenko had stabbed herself, wouldn't the\n"
"sickle still be inside the cage?"
msgstr ""

#. お、驚きのあまり…
#. 入間ちゃんがまともな意見を…っ！
msgctxt "0063 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid "O-Omigod! Miu actually said something smart!"
msgstr ""

#. もしかしたら…
#. 床板が外れていた理由はそれかもしれないネ。
msgctxt "0064 | c03_217_000 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"Perhaps that explains why the\n"
"floorboard was removed."
msgstr ""

#. 彼女はカマで自分を刺した後、
#. 残った力で凶器を床下に放り投げて処分したんだヨ。
msgctxt "0065 | c03_217_000 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"After stabbing herself with the sickle,\n"
"she threw it underneath the floor."
msgstr ""

#. 床板は、凶器のカマを処分する為に、
#. あいつ自身が外したって訳か…
msgctxt "0066 | c03_217_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"So she took off the floorboard to\n"
"get rid of the sickle...?"
msgstr ""

#. 確かに…そう考えると納得できるかも。
msgctxt "0067 | c03_217_000 | C004_Gokuh"
msgid "Yes... That make sense to Gonta..."
msgstr ""

#. な、納得などできんっ！
msgctxt "0068 | c03_217_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "W-Well it doesn't make sense to me!"
msgstr ""

#. 自殺する理由がないではないか！
#. なぜ、転子が自殺などするんじゃ！
msgctxt "0069 | c03_217_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "There's no reason for Tenko to commit suicide!"
msgstr ""

#. もしかしたら、オレがさっき言った事も
#. あながち間違いじゃないのかもしれないね？
msgctxt "0070 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"Maybe I wasn't too far off with the theory\n"
"I had earlier..."
msgstr ""

#. …茶柱ちゃんがアンジーちゃんを殺したってヤツだよ。
msgctxt "0071 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid "Y'know, about Tenko killing Angie?"
msgstr ""

#. …んあ？
msgctxt "0072 | c03_217_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "Nyeh?"
msgstr ""

#. ほら、茶柱ちゃんとアンジーちゃんって、
#. よく夢野ちゃんを取り合って揉めてたでしょ？
msgctxt "0073 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"Because Tenko and Angie were fighting for\n"
"your attention, right?"
msgstr ""

#. アンジーさんの仕業ですね！
#. いつの間に、夢野さんを洗脳したんですかっ！？
msgctxt "0074 | c03_217_000 | C011_Chaba"
msgid "Hey, Angie! When did you brainwash Himiko!?"
msgstr ""

#. そんな積もり積もった想いが
#. 茶柱ちゃんを凶行に走らせたものの…
msgctxt "0075 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"Tenko's pent-up frustration led her to\n"
"commit such an atrocity..."
msgstr ""

#. 結局は、良心の呵責に苛まれて、
#. 彼女は自殺しちゃったんだ。
msgctxt "0076 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"Her conscience couldn't handle it anymore, \n"
"so she decided to end her own life."
msgstr ""

#. な、なん…じゃと…？
msgctxt "0077 | c03_217_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "Wh-What...?"
msgstr ""

#. けどよ…あいつが自殺だとしたら、
#. なんでわざわざ降霊術中に死んだんだ？
msgctxt "0078 | c03_217_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"But...if she was gonna kill herself,\n"
"why do it during the seance?"
msgstr ""

#. もちろん、自分の死の真相を隠す為だよ。
msgctxt "0079 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid "She wanted to hide the truth of her suicide."
msgstr ""

#. な、なんの為に…？
msgctxt "0080 | c03_217_000 | C012_Shiro"
msgid "R-Really? Why?"
msgstr ""

#. このコロシアイゲームで、
#. 自殺の真相を隠す理由なんて１つしかないよね？
msgctxt "0081 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"There could only be one reason to hide it \n"
"in a killing game, right?"
msgstr ""

#. みんなを<CLT=cltSTRONG>道連れ<CLT=cltNORMAL>にする為だよ。
msgctxt "0082 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid "It's to <CLT=cltSTRONG>take us down with her<CLT=cltNORMAL>."
msgstr ""

#. …道連れ？
msgctxt "0083 | c03_217_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "Take us down...?"
msgstr ""

#. 彼女は自分の死の真相を隠し、
#. オレらに学級裁判で間違った答えを出させる事で…
msgctxt "0084 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"She wanted us to pick the wrong\n"
"answer during the class trial..."
msgstr ""

#. みんなを道連れにしようとしたんだ！
#. つまり、これは一種の無理心中なんだよ！
msgctxt "0085 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"...so she could bring us all down!\n"
"She wanted us to die with her!"
msgstr ""

#. まぁ…本当に心中したかった相手は、
#. 夢野ちゃんだけかもしれないけどさ…
msgctxt "0086 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"Okay, well, she probably just wanted Himiko\n"
"to die with her. But still..."
msgstr ""

#. な、何を…言っておる。
#. 転子は…そんなヤツではない。
msgctxt "0087 | c03_217_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid ""
"Wh-What are you saying?\n"
"Tenko...wasn't like that."
msgstr ""

#. だって…あやつはウチに言ったんじゃ！
msgctxt "0088 | c03_217_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "She told me..."
msgstr ""

#. ちゃんと前に向かって生きてください。
#. <CLT=cltSTRONG>“転子や他のみんなと一緒に”<CLT=cltNORMAL>生き残ってください。
msgctxt "0089 | c03_217_000 | C011_Chaba"
msgid ""
"Keep your chin up and live life facing forward!\n"
"Survive <CLT=cltSTRONG>with me and everyone else<CLT=cltNORMAL>!"
msgstr ""

#. その言葉が嘘だとしたら？
msgctxt "0090 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid "What if all of that was just a lie?"
msgstr ""

#. う、嘘…？
msgctxt "0091 | c03_217_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "A lie...?"
msgstr ""

#. 待ってよ！　茶柱さんの最期の言葉なんだよ！？
#. 信じてあげようよ！
msgctxt "0092 | c03_217_000 | C004_Gokuh"
msgid "Wait! We should believe Tenko's last words!"
msgstr ""

#. そう簡単に信じられないのが、
#. この学級裁判の恐ろしいところだよネ。
msgctxt "0093 | c03_217_000 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"The true terror of class trials is that \n"
"you shouldn't believe everything said."
msgstr ""

#. さっき、夢野ちゃんは茶柱ちゃんの事を
#. 『そんなヤツじゃない』って言ってたけどさ…
msgctxt "0094 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"Himiko, you said that Tenko would never\n"
"do anything like that..."
msgstr ""

#. どうして、そんな事が言えるの？
#. キミ達にお互いの何がわかるの？
msgctxt "0095 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"But how can you be so sure?\n"
"Did you guys *actually* know each other?"
msgstr ""

#. 春川ちゃんが人殺しなのを隠していたみたいに、
#. まだ隠し事をしているヤツだっているはずだよ？
msgctxt "0096 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"People keep all sorts of secrets, like Maki. She\n"
"hid the fact that she's a cold-blooded killer."
msgstr ""

#. この場にいる人を完全に信じる事なんて
#. オレらにはできないはずだよ…？
msgctxt "0097 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"Is it wise of us to trust other people\n"
"wholeheartedly in this kind of situation?"
msgstr ""

#. …ったく、テメーはピュアな野郎だな。
msgctxt "0098 | c03_217_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid "Geez...you're such a naive dude."
msgstr ""

#. …ピュア？
msgctxt "0099 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid "...Naive?"
msgstr ""

#. オレらは生の人間同士だ…作りモノじゃねーんだぞ。
#. 隠し事くらいはあたりめーだろーが。
msgctxt "0100 | c03_217_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"We're all just people, y'know? Of course\n"
"we're gonna have some secrets."
msgstr ""

#. 問題は…そこに悪意があるかどうかだ。
msgctxt "0101 | c03_217_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"What matters is whether there's any malice\n"
"behind 'em."
msgstr ""

#. 悪意があるかどうかなんて、
#. いくらでも嘘をつけるよね？
msgctxt "0102 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"People can lie about how malicious\n"
"their hidden secrets really are."
msgstr ""

#. それもあたりめーだ。
#. 他人の事はいくら考えてもわからねーからな。
msgctxt "0103 | c03_217_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"Well duh. It's impossible to know for\n"
"sure what others are thinking."
msgstr ""

#. だからこそ、自分がどうしてーかだ！
#. 自分が信じてーかどうかで決めるしかねーんだよ！
msgctxt "0104 | c03_217_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"That's why it all comes down to whether \n"
"or not you believe in yourself!"
msgstr ""

#. 裏切られても相手のせいじゃねー！
#. そいつを信じるって決めた自分のせいだ！
msgctxt "0105 | c03_217_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"If you get betrayed, it's not their fault!\n"
"It's your fault for believing in them!"
msgstr ""

#. オレがハルマキを信じたのもそういう理由だぜ！
#. オレがこいつを信じてーって思ったからだ！
msgctxt "0106 | c03_217_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"That's why I believed in Maki Roll!\n"
"Because I wanted to believe in her!"
msgstr ""

#. …カッコつけたところで、
#. トレーニング休んだ事は帳消しにならないからね。
msgctxt "0107 | c03_217_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"Just because you're acting all cool\n"
"doesn't mean you get to skip training."
msgstr ""

#. な、なんだよ…ちっと厳し過ぎねーか？
msgctxt "0108 | c03_217_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"H-Hey, c'mon... Don'tcha think you're\n"
"being a little too strict?"
msgstr ""

#. まぁ、百田ちゃんとオレの話が合わないのは、
#. 最初から諦めているけど…
msgctxt "0109 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"Well, we come from different backgrounds.\n"
"So for now, let's agree to disagree."
msgstr ""

#. ピュアなんて言われたのは初めてだよ。
#. オレみたいな嘘つきがさ。
msgctxt "0110 | c03_217_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"No one's ever called me naive before.\n"
"And from Kaito? Seriously?"
msgstr ""

#. ………………
msgctxt "0111 | c03_217_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. 自分が信じたいかどうか…
msgctxt "0112 | c03_217_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "Whether or not I believe..."
msgstr ""

#. もう…ウチの想いは転子には届かんが、
#. それでもウチは転子を信じたい…
msgctxt "0113 | c03_217_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid ""
"My heart...can't reach Tenko anymore... \n"
"But I wanna believe in her..."
msgstr ""

#. あやつは自殺なんてするヤツではない！
#. ウチらを道連れにするようなヤツではない！
msgctxt "0114 | c03_217_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid ""
"She wouldn't commit suicide!\n"
"She wouldn't try to take us down!"
msgstr ""

#. ウチは、それを信じたいぞ！
msgctxt "0115 | c03_217_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "That's what I want to believe!"
msgstr ""

#. うん、ゴン太もだよ。
#. 茶柱さんが自殺なんて信じられないもん。
msgctxt "0116 | c03_217_000 | C004_Gokuh"
msgid ""
"Me too. Gonta no can believe Tenko commit\n"
"suicide."
msgstr ""

#. でも、茶柱が自殺だって考えると、
#. すべてに納得できるのも確かだよ？
msgctxt "0117 | c03_217_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"But if Tenko did commit suicide, that would\n"
"answer all of our questions."
msgstr ""

#. それでも茶柱さんを信じろと言うなら、
#. それなりの根拠を示して貰いたいネ…
msgctxt "0118 | c03_217_000 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"If you insist we believe in Tenko,\n"
"then provide a reason to do so."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>ちゃんとした根拠…か。
msgctxt "0119 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "<CLT=cltMIND>A proper reason..."
msgstr ""

#. わかったよ、根拠を示せばいいんだね。
msgctxt "0120 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "Alright...I'll give you a reason."
msgstr ""

#. …そんなものがあるの？
msgctxt "0121 | c03_217_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid "...Is there a reason?"
msgstr ""

#. うん、もちろんあるよ…
#. だから、春川さんも僕を信用してくれないかな？
msgctxt "0122 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "Yes, there is. Will you trust me, Maki?"
msgstr ""

#. 後でそれが間違いだったとわかったら、
#. その時は好きに言ってくれて構わないから…
msgctxt "0123 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"If it turns out I'm wrong, you can\n"
"blame me all you like."
msgstr ""

#. 今だけは、僕の探偵としての考えを信じて欲しいんだ。
msgctxt "0124 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"But for now...I need you to trust\n"
"in my detective work."
msgstr ""

#. ………………
msgctxt "0125 | c03_217_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. <CLT=cltMIND>僕も…茶柱さんが自殺なんて信じられない。
#. だって、彼女は…
msgctxt "0126 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>I don't believe Tenko would kill\n"
"herself. Because of what she said..."
msgstr ""

#. それでは、みなさん！
#. また降霊術の後でお会いしましょう！
msgctxt "0127 | c03_217_000 | C011_Chaba"
msgid ""
"Okay, everyone!\n"
"I'll see you guys after the seance!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>あの時、彼女は<CLT=cltSTRONG>『また後で』<CLT=cltMIND>って言ってた。
#. その彼女が自殺を決意していたなんて信じられない。
msgctxt "0128 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>She said <CLT=cltSTRONG>\"see you guys after.\"<CLT=cltMIND>\n"
"I doubt she had a sudden change of heart."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>彼女がどうやって殺されたのかわからないからって、
#. 自殺なんて答えに逃げちゃダメなんだ。
msgctxt "0129 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>Just because we don't know how she\n"
"was killed doesn't mean that it was suicide."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>もっとみんなで話し合えば、
#. きっと別の真相が見えてくるはずなんだ…
msgctxt "0130 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>We shouldn't be satisfied with that.\n"
"And if we keep thinking, we'll find the truth."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>その為にも…まずは茶柱さんの事を信じよう！
msgctxt "0131 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>And that means...\n"
"we have to believe in Tenko!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>いや…僕がみんなに信じさせないといけないんだ！
msgctxt "0132 | c03_217_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "<CLT=cltMIND>I'll make them all believe!"
msgstr ""
